# Plans Directory

Store persistent task plans here for multi-session work.

## Structure

```
plans/
├── feature-name/
│   ├── requirements.md      # User requirements
│   ├── parallel-plan.md     # Task breakdown
│   └── shared.md            # Cross-task context
└── quick-plans/
    └── simple-task.md       # Lightweight plans
```

## Usage

1. Create plan before starting complex work
2. Reference via `@.docs/plans/feature/parallel-plan.md`
3. Continue across sessions without context loss
